3. cs.SI (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a decoding scheme to improve error-correction performance, which is a topic related to control systems. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new algorithmic scheme for decoding, which falls under the scope of data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses channel coding schemes, which are used in communication networks, and proposes a decoding scheme to improve error-correction performance, which is a topic related to networking and internet architecture.
